      • dump

        public void dump(byte[] data,
                 int offset,
                 int size,
                 java.io.PrintStream out)
        Decodes the escher stream from a byte array and dumps the results to a print stream.(从字节数组中解码escher流并将结果转储到打印流。)
        Parameters:
        data - The data array containing the escher records.(data -包含escher记录的数据数组。)
        offset - The starting offset within the data array.(odge-数据数组内的开始偏差。)
        size - The number of bytes to read.(size -要读取的字节数。)
        out - The output stream to write the results to.(out -要将结果写入的输出流。)
